Developer Terms of Use
des: Positive Energy skill provides positive thoughts for you to take throughout the day. Alexa will say positive sentences to inspire and energize your mind. Our thoughts shape our actions. When you hear positive thoughts, it will gently influence your mind to think positively. After hearing the quote you can say "tell me one more", to listen to another quote. More frequent you hear the positive thoughts, the better.
